Barroso: Commission Adopted Financial-Transaction Tax Proposal

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 
2011-09-28T07:28:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/barroso-commission-adopted-financial-transaction-tax-proposal.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said the commission today adopted a proposal for
introducing a financial-transaction tax.  The fiancial sector must make a contribution back to
society, Barroso told the European Parliament in Strasbourg,
 France .  To contact the reporter on this story:
